name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: Money should be a by product of your businesses’ purpose - all our investors are in top decile and quartile, while maintaining their return profiles. Being good makes more money. Acc to Tom Van Dyck @RBC #FuquaSBSI https://t.co/JJfFszvEqO
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: We differentiate between ESG and impact investing, which is tangible measurable improvements in societal needs- @bethbaff @calvertimpcap moving from outputs to outcomes is a trend we see #fuquasbsi https://t.co/ZnKuhIH7N2
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: Part of reporting challenge is companies aren’t disclosing important metrics- carbon emissions, DEI metrics. We see  shareholders exercising their power to drive transparency, e.g 530 shareholder resolutions in last year. — Tom Van Dyck #fuquasbsi
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: We’ve mapped all of our investments across sectors, UN SDGs, and IRIS metrics. This helps our investors understand and compare our impact. And we customize metrics with investees as well. - @bethbaff #fuquasbsi
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: We have developed proprietary scorecards to help cos in frontier markets to start to disclose info on gender equity and climate. We focus on parts of business that are material to the company. Cost and efficiency of impact measurement is key. - Anne Park #fuquasbsi
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: We help investors explore and improve practices around DEI factors in their own practices as well as system level changes    so they don’t lose value due to bias. We’re a fund of funds so we can influence funds. - Joanna Kuang #fuquasbsi
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: We see impact data as a continuous improvement tool rather than a compliance tool - Joanna Kuang @IllumenCapital #fuquasbsi
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: Challenges of impact management? Intellectuality of frameworks vs translation to effective implementation. Ultimately, this needs to be consumer and investor friendly. @bethbaff #fuquasbsi
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: Challenges? Greenwashing will taint perception of returns. Nuance matters. Not all impact is the same. Not all ESG labeled funds actually discern ESG risks well. Beware of this! - Tom Van Dyck @RBC
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: “I can’t believe what you say because I see what you do” Daryn Dodson quoting James Baldwin - in this case referrring to on number of women and people of color invested in by endowments vs what they say about DEI. #fuquasbsi #gap
name: Cathy Clark #impinv

full_text: What students can do: Ask for ESG options in your 401k , pay attention to how you shop, how you invest. -Tom Van Dyck @RBC
